{"tid":816443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港豬澳今次真係難逃一劫....","createTime":"2018-09-12T17:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T05:40:23.000Z","uid":90953,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a95f0bbd74d3c1d1e77f7a55c6f625c58040f3","tid":816443,"uid":90953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T17:56:53.000Z","msg":"颶風伊莎貝爾（英語：Hurricane Isabel）是2003年大西洋颶風季期間最強烈，造成損失最慘重，死亡人數最多的颶風，也是該季第9個獲得命名的風暴，第5個颶風和第2個大型颶風，於9月6日在大西洋熱帶海域的佛得角附近由一股東風波形成。系統朝西北方向前進，進入一片水溫較高，風切變很弱的環境後穩步加強，於9月11日達到風速<span style=\"color: red;\">每小時270公里</span>的最高強度。經過四天的強度波動後，颶風逐漸減弱，於9月18日在北卡羅萊納州的外灘群島以風速每小時165公里的強度登陸。風暴登陸後迅速減弱，於次日在賓夕法尼亞州西部轉變為溫帶氣旋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/015554_3589b7f3403b8cf88cc2e09bc2f05257.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F015554_3589b7f3403b8cf88cc2e09bc2f05257.png&h=b5e81887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n颶風伊莎貝爾對屏障島造成的破壞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hurricane_Isabel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FHurricane_Isabel&d=Q%2FdHQiWXcl66RpyTsZ%2FmRJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3374742c\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hurricane_Isabel</a><br />\n<br />\n美軍的聯合颱風警報中心已經將「山竹」評定為「5級颶風」，依美國採用的1分鐘平均風力標準，中心風力達到每小時150海里（<span style=\"color: red;\">時速約278 公里</span>），比目前大西洋海面上的4級颶風「佛羅倫斯」的120海里（時速約222公里）還要高出一大截。聯合颱風警報中心預計，「山竹」強度將會再稍為提升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E6%92%B2%E8%BF%91-%E5%8D%87%E6%A0%BC-5%E7%B4%9A%E9%A2%B6%E9%A2%A8-%E9%A2%A8%E9%80%9F%E9%81%94278%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C-%E6%88%96%E9%A2%A8%E7%9C%BC%E7%BD%AE%E6%8F%9B%E5%86%8D%E8%BF%8E%E5%B7%94%E5%B3%B0-082800145.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25AB%25B9%25E6%2592%25B2%25E8%25BF%2591-%25E5%258D%2587%25E6%25A0%25BC-5%25E7%25B4%259A%25E9%25A2%25B6%25E9%25A2%25A8-%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%2581%2594278%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2587%258C-%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E7%259C%25BC%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E6%258F%259B%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25BF%258E%25E5%25B7%2594%25E5%25B3%25B0-082800145.html&d=Q%2FdHQiWXcl66RpyTsZ%2FmRJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b48dcef3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E6%92%B2%E8%BF%91-%E5%8D%87%E6%A0%BC-5%E7%B4%9A%E9%A2%B6%E9%A2%A8-%E9%A2%A8%E9%80%9F%E9%81%94278%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C-%E6%88%96%E9%A2%A8%E7%9C%BC%E7%BD%AE%E6%8F%9B%E5%86%8D%E8%BF%8E%E5%B7%94%E5%B3%B0-082800145.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdfd0ecc37ea7e01a61c1e71a5aa651b1e1103a9","tid":816443,"uid":90953,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/020447_df8528afc725901ad817c74c6f0a10a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F020447_df8528afc725901ad817c74c6f0a10a5.png&h=b1d3c9a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f94345eeb4d48bdbe6924f39321c4a84ab9257","tid":816443,"uid":90953,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:07:55.000Z","msg":"有三個情況好大機會發生<br />\n<br />\n人工島沖散<br />\n海水倒灌<br />\n斷橋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a23a01cffc8476a1fe9d54de1aa8d515b1e3f3e","tid":816443,"uid":164240,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"吹正先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bef8509ee64d47abd7